			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2510169">
									

<p>Good news everyone! We found a way to make Portland even weirder!</p>
<p>In all seriousness, when you first told me that you were doing a PL/Maxwellist/Anderson Robotics tale, I was excited. Then you shelved the idea, and I was sad. Then you unshelved the idea and came up with this gem, and I was thrilled.</p>
<p>There is a lot for me to love here. Between the likable characters, the references to AR, the world building, and the creation of Three Portlands, this is a all around great tale. I can't wait to see you use Three Portlands again, and to use it in my own work as well.</p>
<p>+1.</p>

							</div>

								
					
